column1: Delivery Area Surcharge Destination ZIP Code Listing
A Delivery Area Surcharge applies to Air and Ground packages
delivered to higher cost-to-serve ZIP Codes.
The surcharge is $2.10 per package for residential addresses
Note: This format has dropped the leading zero. For the 4 digit numbers
a 0 should be added. For example, the first zip code shown as 1005 should read as 01005.
